戴夫·马修斯（Dave Matthews）在“家庭重症疾病”之后退出福利音乐会https://www.nme.com/news/music/dave-matthews-benefit-concert-withdraws-critical-illness-family-3833072?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=dave-matthews-benefit-concert-withdraws-critical-疾病家庭Daniel PetersThu, 30 Jan 2025 06:06:35 +0000 Music NewsNewsRockhttps://www.nme.com/?p=3833072 <p><img width="1392" height="884" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/DaveMatthews-2024-Getty.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="戴夫·马修斯（Dave Matthews）" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/DaveMatthews-2024-Getty.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/DaveMatthews-2024-Getty-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/DaveMatthews-2024-Getty-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/DaveMatthews-2024-Getty-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/DaveMatthews-2024-Getty-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 1392px) 100vw, 1392px" /></p><p>本周早些时候，戴夫·马修斯乐队（Dave Matthews Band）宣布了一段漫长的2025夏季旅行跋涉</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/dave-matthews-benefit-concert-withdraws-critical-illness-family-3833072">戴夫·马修斯（Dave Matthews）在“家庭中的重症疾​​病”之后退出福利音乐会，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="1392" height="884" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/DaveMatthews-2024-Getty.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="戴夫·马修斯（Dave Matthews）" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/DaveMatthews-2024-Getty.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/DaveMatthews-2024-Getty-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/DaveMatthews-2024-Getty-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/DaveMatthews-2024-Getty-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/DaveMatthews-2024-Getty-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 1392px) 100vw, 1392px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dave-matthews">戴夫·马修斯（Dave Matthews）</a>由于“家庭中的重症疾​​病”而撤回了迫在眉睫的野火福利音乐会。</p><p>马修斯（Matthews）将与约翰·梅耶（John Mayer）一起在FireAid演出 - <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/benefit-concert-for-victims-of-los-angeles-wildfires-announced-3828097">该活动首次于本月早些时候宣布，</a>以支持<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/entertainment-world-reacts-to-heart-wrenching-los-angeles-wildfires-3827340">毁灭性洛杉矶野火的受害者</a>，该活动将于今天（1月30日）在Intuit Dome和起亚论坛上同时举行。 ，后一个场地最初是为了接待Matthews。</p><p>一份声明说：“由于家庭的重症病重，戴夫·马修斯（Dave Matthews）不幸的是，本周无法在火灾中表现出来，音乐人则受益。”</p><p>起亚论坛表演将与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/alanis-morissette">Alanis Morissette</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/anderson-paak">Anderson .Paak</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/red-hot-chilli-peppers">，</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/stephen-stills">Graham</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/graham-nash">Nash</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/stevie-nicks">，</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/green-day">Green Day</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/john-fogerty">John Fogerty</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/joni-mitchell">Joni Mitchell</a>一起进行，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/no-doubt">毫无疑问</a>， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/pink">P！</a>其他的。</p><p> On Tuesday (January 28), <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dave-matthews-band">Dave Matthews Band</a> announced a 2025 summer tour, which notably includes a concert at the Kia Forum on August 22. Tickets will be released on February 21 at 10am local time, while a presale is currently underway for members of仓库<a href="https://davematthewsband.com/warehouse" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在这里</a>。</p><p>请参阅下面的完整列表，其中还包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fall-out-boy-luke-combs-dave-matthews-band-announced-headliners-boston-calling-2025-festival-tickets-3826554">先前宣布的波士顿呼叫节</a>。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-in