nde">Ariana Grande</a> , Billie Eilish and more <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/entertainment-world-reacts-to-heart-wrenching-los-angeles-wildfires-3827340">have reacted to the “heart-wrenching” devastation caused by the wildfires</a> , sharing resource links for those in need of help.</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/la-music-community-tragic-wildfires-long-lasting-effects-3828259">Members of the LA music community have also spoken to <i>NME</i> about being hit hard</a> , with a number of venues, studios and artists being affected by the blaze.</p></div></div><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/dave-matthews-benefit-concert-withdraws-critical-illness-family-3833072">戴夫·马修斯（Dave Matthews）在“家庭中的重症疾​​病”之后退出福利音乐会，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
麦当娜在纽约喜剧俱乐部表演惊喜站立https://www.nme.com/news/music/madonna-performs-stand-up-set-at-new-york-comedy-club-3833070?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=madonna-performs-stand-up-新的York-Comedy-ClubDaniel Peters Thu, 30 Jan 2025 04:28:18 +0000 Music NewsNewsPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3833070 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/madonna@2000x1270-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="麦当娜在舞台上表演" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/madonna@2000x1270-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/madonna@2000x1270-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/madonna@2000x1270-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/madonna@2000x1270-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/madonna@2000x1270-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/madonna@2000x1270-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “她很有趣！她有开玩笑。她有话要说。她喝了茶，”她的喜剧演员朋友艾米·舒默（Amy Schumer）</p><p>麦当娜（Post Madonna）在纽约喜剧俱乐部（NME）首次出现在纽约喜剧俱乐部<a href="https://www.nme.com">（NME）</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/madonna-performs-stand-up-set-at-new-york-comedy-club-3833070">上表演惊喜站立</a>。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/madonna@2000x1270-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="麦当娜在舞台上表演" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/madonna@2000x1270-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/madonna@2000x1270-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/madonna@2000x1270-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/madonna@2000x1270-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/madonna@2000x1270-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/madonna@2000x1270-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>最近，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/madonna">麦当娜（Madonna）</a>在纽约喜剧俱乐部（New York Comedy Club）表演了一个惊喜站立。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/madonna-pays-tribute-to-friend-who-saved-her-life-after-she-passed-out-on-bathroom-floor-and-woke-up-in-icu-3560359">麦当娜直播伦敦：流行女王与她的遗产斗争</a></strong></li></ul><p>据报道，据报道，流行偶像是在上周六（1月25日）在喜剧酒窖上看到的，随后是朋友和喜剧演员<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/amy-schumer">艾米·舒默（Amy Schumer）</a>的设置，在<a href="https://www.the-sun.com/entertainment/13389843/madonna-comedy-club-standup-gig-foul-mouthed-trump-diss/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>麦克风</em></a>前进行了半小时的尝试，他的消息人士补充说，听众“是”她的出现使她感到震惊。</p><p> “She didn&#39;t do as well as you&#39;d think she would, she got laughs every time she dropped F-bomb, because just hearing Madonna curse is funny,” the source told <em>The Sun</em> , also claiming that the set included a <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/donald-trump">Donald特朗普</a>笑话。</p><p>那天晚上之后，舒默与麦当娜在俱乐部桌子上分享了一张自拍照，上面写着“这张桌子仅为喜剧窖喜剧演员保留。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DFTKIIYOVqz/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border